# Patterns (one per line) lychee excludes from the offline link check (.github/workflows/markdown.yml).
#
# Vite copies public/ to the deploy root, so public/data/projects.json is served at the
# deployed URL /data/projects.json (linked from colophon.html). That URL is valid in
# production, but lychee runs offline with --root-dir at the repo root, where the file is
# under public/ — so it cannot resolve it. Exclude narrow public-served paths.
data/projects\.json
content/resume\.md
content/research-statement\.md
content/summary\.md
